abstract: Militants in Egypt loyal to Islamic State claim they captured American-made M60 tank engine after ambushing Egyptian military; identifying themselves as Sinai Province of the Islamic State, group posted six pictures on Twitter of what looks like engine; spokesman for Egyptian armed forces counters no engine was taken.
lead_paragraph: Militants identifying themselves as the Sinai Province of the Islamic State said Monday that they had captured the engine of an American-made M60 tank from the Egyptian military in an ambush.

headline.print_headline: Middle East; Egypt: Militants Claim Ambush
